title: Chelsea Clinton Gets Ambushed About ‘Real Father’ During Book Signing Event
text: What should have been an exciting time for former First Daughter Chelsea Clinton was met with some harsh questions as she attended a book signing event at Book People, in Austin, Texas, on Friday. The 35-year-old attended the event to promote her new book when an activist questioned the paternity of her father, Bill Clinton....
